XiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c4a24926\" target=\"_blank\">http://bochk.com/tc/mortgage/tools/freevaluation.html</a><br />\n<br />\n留意網上估價與實地銀行會有出入<br />\n<br />\n按揭成數及條例 <a href=\"https://www.midland.com.hk/calculator/new-measures-on-mortgage.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.midland.com.hk%2Fcalculator%2Fnew-measures-on-mortgage.jsp&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1c61535e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.midland.com.hk/calculator/new-measures-on-mortgage.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n兇宅查詢 <a href=\"http://property.hk/unlucky.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproperty.hk%2Funlucky.php&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1a1882e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://property.hk/unlucky.php</a><br />\n<br />\n有關傢私買賣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://furniture.28hse.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffurniture.28hse.com&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=13029856\" target=\"_blank\">http://furniture.28hse.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ikea.com/hk/zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fikea.com%2Fhk%2Fzh&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2de51d13\" target=\"_blank\">http://ikea.com/hk/zh</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://innshops.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finnshops.com&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=61c93867\" target=\"_blank\">http://innshops.com</a><br />\n<br />\n另外上強國訂做購買可以平啲<br />\n<br />\n裝修類<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://guanre.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguanre.com&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0ed0be42\" target=\"_blank\">http://guanre.com</a> 香港裝修黃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://decocare.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdecocare.com&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=753d0ad9\" target=\"_blank\">http://decocare.com</a> 裝修網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkdecoman.com/jsp/main.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkdecoman.com%2Fjsp%2Fmain.jsp&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=001f5bf5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkdecoman.com/jsp/main.jsp</a> 裝修佬 <br />\n<br />\n以上並非推薦<br />\n<br />\n按揭保險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkmc.com.hk/chi/our_business/mortgage_insurance_programme.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmc.com.hk%2Fchi%2Four_business%2Fmortgage_insurance_programme.html&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f1802059\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkmc.com.hk/chi/our_business/mortgage_insurance_programme.html</a><br />\n<br />\n印花稅計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/stamp/stamp_duty_rates.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Ftaxes%2Fstamp%2Fstamp_duty_rates.htm&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6ccbd1e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/stamp/stamp_duty_rates.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n男女朋友 可以未婚夫妻名義做按揭<br />\n<br />\n放租要5成按揭<br />\n<br />\ncash rebate 1% vs 1.x% <br />\n<br />\n簡單而言：例子買4m樓，借3.6m<br />\n<br />\n1. 手頭緊： 揀1%cash, loan size 借足 再extra 比1%cash （即 4mx0.6x1% = 24,000)<br />\n<br />\n2. 手頭唔緊： 揀回1.6%， 扣Loan size , 自己成交要比多1.6% 既錢 佢1個月內回返比你 變相同eg1 既loan size 少左 1.6%， 利息少D <br />\n（即 4m x 0.6x 1.6% = 38,400，比起例子1，你成交果陣暫時要比多38,400， 銀行一個月內退返比你）<br />\n<br />\nP.s : 每間銀行計法大致一樣，但都有唔同，例如IXBX, 佢既1.6係多過其他行，詳情問banker<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n置業POST 鐵三角<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/100545_2c5cb87e1d5b576d5a3a71310d8e8e33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F100545_2c5cb87e1d5b576d5a3a71310d8e8e33.jpg&h=327f07fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n置業POST 係時候加入林太敬拜重溫經典<br />\n林太豪氣回應，「290萬已經最低，我個仔買貴40萬冇咩問題，佢要住㗎嘛，如果升又點呢。阿仔買嘅單位，銀行估到價，銀行唔會死錯人嘅，嗰啲咁既專家，食屎啦！我哋唔係有見地，我哋係腳踏實地，唔聽專家㗎，聽專家意見就死啦。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=cd560601\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&h=1154b792\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/100600_c2e09a7b5958bf79ab615df3c9244a48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F100600_c2e09a7b5958bf79ab615df3c9244a48.jpg&h=2ed63459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時係買樓時機？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/100611_090360ff0b029b1f57ca40fe2926c68a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F100611_090360ff0b029b1f57ca40fe2926c68a.png&h=6c537c62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/100612_b0f1496fd73d036205628c24b24bb772.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F100612_b0f1496fd73d036205628c24b24bb772.png&h=0cf7a669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fb67ec045b18507c77ad946715158918563eeb","tid":544043,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:51:20.000Z","msg":"又爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eca1d0ba74e410c98bd182d46d2fae76d4e9974","tid":544043,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"舊post 都無時間追<im